# pipenv
#   According to pypa/pipenv#1198, it is recommended to include Pipfile.lock in version control.
#   However, in cases where the author of a package wants to allow users to use their own Pipfile.lock:
#Pipfile.lock

# poetry
#   Signifies the layout of the dependency tree
#   Like Pipfile.lock, poetry.lock is generally recommended to be committed.
#poetry.lock

# pdm
#   Like Pipfile.lock, pdm.lock is generally recommended to be committed.
